HEADWORD: Moidore
<hw>Moi"dore</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pg. <ets>moeda
d'ouro</ets>, lit., coin of gold. Cf. <er>Money</er>, and
<er>Aureate</er>.]</ety> <def>A gold coin of Portugal, valued at about
27s. sterling.</def>⟦br⟧
